@host = http://localhost:5176

### Tạo MonthlyReading với upload ảnh
POST {{host}}/api/MonthlyReadings
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="CycleId"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ElectricOld"

100
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ElectricNew"

150
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="WaterOld"

50
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="WaterNew"

75
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Status"

Pending
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### Lấy MonthlyReading theo ID
GET {{host}}/api/MonthlyReadings/1

###

### Lấy danh sách MonthlyReadings theo CycleId
GET {{host}}/api/MonthlyReadings/by-cycle/1

###

